### NEJM publication

###   

Despite **158 citations** on [Google Scholar](https://scholar.google.com/scholar?cites=4013341607831507270&as_sdt=2005&sciodt=0,5&hl=en), and a **lot of tweets**, I didn’t find **anyone critical** of this publication, until the Lancet scandal.

